-- Turkey's Bank Asya shares to resume trade on Monday
-- By Can Sezer
-- Mon Sep 15, 2014 02:23AM EDT
-- None



ISTANBUL, Sept 15 (Reuters) - Trading in the shares of Turkey's Islamic lender Bank Asya <ASYAB.IS> will resume in Istanbul on Monday morning, Borsa Istanbul said in a statement.

The shares were suspended on Aug. 7.